[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_19",
    "text": "新成就 新跨越",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.3422900024207214,
      0.06702208682406702,
      0.6942628903413217,
      0.18888042650418888
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_0",
    "text": "“十一五”期间，农垦系统以科学发展观 为统领，积极应对自然灾害和国际金融危机 造成的严重困难和挑战，加快转变发展方式， 大力提升农产品有效供给能力，经济社会全 面协调快速发展，现代农业建设实现新跨越， 亮点纷呈。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04841442749939482,
      0.06736058221206737,
      0.2570806100217865,
      0.12524329356012523
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_28",
    "text": "结构调整更趋科学",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.7765674170902929,
      0.06837606837606838,
      0.9377874606632777,
      0.08462384700008463
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_29",
    "text": "“十一五”时期，第一、第二、第三产业增加 值在农垦生产总值中的比重更趋科学合理，分 别由“十五”期末的41.2%、30.7%、28.1%调整为 33.3%、40.9%、25.8%。在粮、棉、胶等产业培育 了一批大型骨干龙头企业。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7741466957153231,
      0.08902428704408902,
      0.9518276446381021,
      0.13133621054413133
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_1",
    "text": "经济发展又好又快",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.07213749697409828,
      0.1381061183041381,
      0.23432582909707092,
      0.15367690615215368
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_30",
    "text": "“五”期间农垦三次产业增加值",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7949648995400629,
      0.13912160446813912,
      0.9290728637133866,
      0.1469069983921469
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_8076765115f6c402e81c6bfb48139bc2_1_31",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.7654320987654321,
